        "description": "{\"blocks\":[{\"key\":\"1h9ib\",\"text\":\"In plants, beautifulness is key to survival. They allure other species to make them reach different environments and be able to grow and survive. However, beauty by itself does not guarantee this. They need other \\\"weapons\\\" to reach further, such as hybridizing with different species and reproducing a lot. Stefano Mancusso explained this in his book The Incredible Journey of Plants.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[{\"offset\":351,\"length\":32,\"style\":\"ITALIC\"}],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}}],\"entityMap\":{}}",
