        "domain": "zIvNmah8LhNAGOHRn1df",
        "description": "{\"blocks\":[{\"key\":\"d4nkq\",\"text\":\"In his book The Incredible Journey of Plants, Stefano Mancuso explains how a date palm tree could germinate after 2,000 years. Archeologist found its seed at the ancient fortress of Masada (Israel). Some scientists provided its seeds the apropiate environment for germination someplace else, and the date palm managed to grow. He argues that many seeds from different species still remain hidden, depending entirely on luck to be found.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[{\"offset\":12,\"length\":32,\"style\":\"ITALIC\"}],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}}],\"entityMap\":{}}"
